[APPLAUSE]

00:00:09.640 --> 00:00:10.410
VIKAS KHANNA: Hi.

00:00:10.410 --> 00:00:11.260
AMAR JOSHI: Nice to
have you at Google.

00:00:11.260 --> 00:00:12.060
Thank you for coming again.

00:00:12.060 --> 00:00:13.143
VIKAS KHANNA: My pleasure.

